sub_title: Manager Geomechanics Experimentation Shell Global Solutions Netherlands
summary:
My professional experience lies both in R&D and in an operational/business environment in Upstream oil & gas. I much enjoy working on high-profile projects with challenging targets and with a multi-disciplinary team. 

Specialties: oil and gas well and reservoir surveillance for field development, petrophysical evaluation, geomechanics for well delivery and containment, well delivery support, integrated reservoir modelling, value of information, staff recruitment and development, team management, contract management
